{"word":"H5812 - עֲזַזְיָהוּ - ʻĂzazyâhûw - az-az-yaw'-hoo - Azaziah","slug":"H5812","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֲזַזְיָהוּ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻĂzazyâhûw"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>az-az-yaw'-hoo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Azaziah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עזזיהוּ</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛ăzazyâhû</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>az-az-yaw'-hoo</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Azaziah = \"Jehovah is mighty\" <ol><li>a Levite musician in the reign of David who played the harp in the procession which brought the ark from Obed-edom to Jerusalem</li><li>a Levite in the reign of king Hezekiah of Judah in charge of the tithes</li><li>father of Hoshea, prince of the tribe of Ephraim when David took the census</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H5810\">H5810</a> and <a href=\"#/H3050\">H3050</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3268\">H3268</a>, <a href=\"#/H3269\">H3269</a>, <a href=\"#/H5794\">H5794</a>, <a href=\"#/H5797\">H5797</a>, <a href=\"#/H5798\">H5798</a>, <a href=\"#/H5802\">H5802</a>, <a href=\"#/H5803\">H5803</a>, <a href=\"#/H5807\">H5807</a>, <a href=\"#/H5808\">H5808</a>, <a href=\"#/H5810\">H5810</a>, <a href=\"#/H5811\">H5811</a>, <a href=\"#/H5813\">H5813</a>, <a href=\"#/H5814\">H5814</a>, <a href=\"#/H5815\">H5815</a>, <a href=\"#/H5816\">H5816</a>, <a href=\"#/H5817\">H5817</a>, <a href=\"#/H5818\">H5818</a>, <a href=\"#/H5819\">H5819</a>, <a href=\"#/H5820\">H5820</a>, <a href=\"#/H5821\">H5821</a>, <a href=\"#/H5822\">H5822</a>"}]}